          "Total Test3 = 5×80 = 400",
          "Other 3 students contribute remaining: 400 - (1.2x + 1.5y)",
          "To minimize x+y, maximize contribution of others → bounded by realistic constraints, giving x+y ≈ 90"
        ],
        "why_correct": {
          "B": "Satisfies total constraints while minimizing combined initial scores."
